[
  {
    "id": "PSA.83.1",
    "book": "Psalms",
    "bookNum": 19,
    "bookAbbrev": "PSA",
    "chapter": 83,
    "verse": 1,
    "text": "[A Song {or} Psalm of Asaph.] Keep not thou silence, O God: hold not thy peace, and be not still, O God. {of Asaph: or, for Asaph}",
    "hash": "96c3d3699894476d43eed57f1bc3143a374201cd3550e9774222273ada829b68"
  },
  {
    "id": "PSA.83.2",
    "book": "Psalms",
    "bookNum": 19,
    "bookAbbrev": "PSA",
    "chapter": 83,
    "verse": 2,
    "text": "For, lo, thine enemies make a tumult: and they that hate thee have lifted up the head.",
    "hash": "d88d6867023d0256b04fe873626d50549d86186e0a9d549a217970f396d8c867"
  },
  {
    "id": "PSA.83.3",
    "book": "Psalms",
    "bookNum": 19,
    "bookAbbrev": "PSA",
    "chapter": 83,
    "verse": 3,
    "text": "They have taken crafty counsel against thy people, and consulted against thy hidden ones.",
    "hash": "d1759fd3ead8e354aa37468f1fc26867c6c9962d5150aa4aaba872fd291019c2"
  },
  {
    "id": "PSA.83.4",
    "book": "Psalms",
    "bookNum": 19,
    "bookAbbrev": "PSA",
    "chapter": 83,
    "verse": 4,
    "text": "They have said, Come, and let us cut them off from {being} a nation; that the name of Israel may be no more in remembrance.",
    "hash": "d78d9f3d01fabc79cc6b23dc932a4327aa000fc4361dfd1bf1c37193cc3b517b"
  },
  {
    "id": "PSA.83.5",
    "book": "Psalms",
    "bookNum": 19,
    "bookAbbrev": "PSA",
    "chapter": 83,
    "verse": 5,
    "text": "For they have consulted together with one consent: they are confederate against thee: {consent: Heb. heart}",
    "hash": "9a6dc8a8ac353227cff7eb583c8f922aa183f0a95c5dad4c059de770f99b787d"
  },
  {
    "id": "PSA.83.6",
    "book": "Psalms",
    "bookNum": 19,
    "bookAbbrev": "PSA",
    "chapter": 83,
    "verse": 6,
    "text": "The tabernacles of Edom, and the Ishmaelites; of Moab, and the Hagarenes;",
    "hash": "11652ba690be02a7acb8698e52bc2913cfbbeb734ab52107c76c6111ff741f40"
  },
  {
    "id": "PSA.83.7",
    "book": "Psalms",
    "bookNum": 19,
    "bookAbbrev": "PSA",
    "chapter": 83,
    "verse": 7,
    "text": "Gebal, and Ammon, and Amalek; the Philistines with the inhabitants of Tyre;",
    "hash": "77615bc36c65d0cbd6af776e3f9f56a312f0ec763c1d95bf5fad0dc11fe372d1"
  },
  {
    "id": "PSA.83.8",
    "book": "Psalms",
    "bookNum": 19,
    "bookAbbrev": "PSA",
    "chapter": 83,
    "verse": 8,
    "text": "Assur also is joined with them: they have holpen the children of Lot. Selah. {holpen: Heb. been an arm to}",
    "hash": "2fab5d422ddd0a2952fccf64c6a0510e8cda5d59f179035f8b03c0ced5de7ee1"
  },
  {
    "id": "PSA.83.9",
    "book": "Psalms",
    "bookNum": 19,
    "bookAbbrev": "PSA",
    "chapter": 83,
    "verse": 9,
    "text": "Do unto them as {unto} the Midianites; as {to} Sisera, as {to} Jabin, at the brook of Kison:",
    "hash": "d4da012734fc9a8846bbddd9196c2c65657b53c05e1395a1ca4e0c8d7826bbb6"
  },
  {
    "id": "PSA.83.10",
    "book": "Psalms",
    "bookNum": 19,
    "bookAbbrev": "PSA",
    "chapter": 83,
    "verse": 10,
    "text": "{Which} perished at Endor: they became {as} dung for the earth.",
    "hash": "dbd1dfb72f52ab3b7f59fd4c2fefef469af5f81ce1a604325f150e333ee99064"
  },
  {
    "id": "PSA.83.11",
    "book": "Psalms",
    "bookNum": 19,
    "bookAbbrev": "PSA",
    "chapter": 83,
    "verse": 11,
    "text": "Make their nobles like Oreb, and like Zeeb: yea, all their princes as Zebah, and as Zalmunna:",
    "hash": "05054f5af0234a9eb532a636f8566f96e5b7ea44404fe4421aeb137f55ac8a55"
  },
  {
    "id": "PSA.83.12",
    "book": "Psalms",
    "bookNum": 19,
    "bookAbbrev": "PSA",
    "chapter": 83,
    "verse": 12,
    "text": "Who said, Let us take to ourselves the houses of God in possession.",
    "hash": "397966a817d833f8e3ca6500d263cb07ad0ea8763452893a1817a3173b06d84a"
  },
  {
    "id": "PSA.83.13",
    "book": "Psalms",
    "bookNum": 19,
    "bookAbbrev": "PSA",
    "chapter": 83,
    "verse": 13,
    "text": "O my God, make them like a wheel; as the stubble before the wind.",
    "hash": "427527014950dcb7663070758b2e43419da853bba54f6aa58a33dbbb9a71c435"
  },
  {
    "id": "PSA.83.14",
    "book": "Psalms",
    "bookNum": 19,
    "bookAbbrev": "PSA",
    "chapter": 83,
    "verse": 14,
    "text": "As the fire burneth a wood, and as the flame setteth the mountains on fire;",
    "hash": "45022ed272c074789591c5ffc6a1cd1015ae98a426c9040cda654a755eb3559f"
  },
  {
    "id": "PSA.83.15",
    "book": "Psalms",
    "bookNum": 19,
    "bookAbbrev": "PSA",
    "chapter": 83,
    "verse": 15,
    "text": "So persecute them with thy tempest, and make them afraid with thy storm.",
    "hash": "192729af51a64b195b9a1ad8b5a5e3bfe6affffbad1b6e7de8a0b35e3f1f7fff"
  },
  {
    "id": "PSA.83.16",
    "book": "Psalms",
    "bookNum": 19,
    "bookAbbrev": "PSA",
    "chapter": 83,
    "verse": 16,
    "text": "Fill their faces with shame; that they may seek thy name, O LORD.",
    "hash": "a0a98c30dc20454cdb7ed760a3c42b67905f4122e0f06f3ffea27a7b30dd0879"
  },
  {
    "id": "PSA.83.17",
    "book": "Psalms",
    "bookNum": 19,
    "bookAbbrev": "PSA",
    "chapter": 83,
    "verse": 17,
    "text": "Let them be confounded and troubled for ever; yea, let them be put to shame, and perish:",
    "hash": "1b656ac692002a3b75aaba61081c90aa3cdb9bb9f4adb3fb23c55d6cee013619"
  },
  {
    "id": "PSA.83.18",
    "book": "Psalms",
    "bookNum": 19,
    "bookAbbrev": "PSA",
    "chapter": 83,
    "verse": 18,
    "text": "That {men} may know that thou, whose name alone {is} JEHOVAH, {art} the most high over all the earth.",
    "hash": "8e62b96f58579f49b250202f130996198f6866e2ae84e0d2657ff2bdf856290a"
  }
]